# ==============================================
# Orbit Web App Environment Variables.
# This is git tracked. DO NOT PUT ANYTHING HERE THAT IS NOT PUBLIC.
# ==============================================
# Note: Expo requires variables to be prefixed with EXPO_PUBLIC_
# to be accessible in the app.
#
# Auth is Better Auth (Google), cookie-based and served by the API — no Supabase.

# -----------------
# API URL (set per command/profile)
# -----------------
# Keep this unset here so you don't need to edit this file repeatedly.
# Use package scripts instead:
# - bun run web:local   (points at http://localhost:3001)
# In production (fly.io) the web app is served same-origin by the API.
